comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bazley's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Harris (ORL) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Krejci (OKC) during the rebound.
Krejci (OKC) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm, which does not affect his ability to make his intended pass.
Pokusevski (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Roby (OKC) makes contact with Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm, which affects his jump shot attempt. The Replay Center confirms that the foul occurs prior to the expiration of the 24 second shot clock.
After setting the pick, Roby (OKC) begins rolling to the basket and incidental contact occurs with Anthony (ORL) as they come together when Anthony goes under the pick.

After the missed shot, Carter Jr. (ORL) has the rebound tapped away by Pokusevski (OKC) when he attempts a putback dunk. Carter Jr.'s (ORL) hand grazes the rim on his follow-through while the ball is in the cylinder, and the contact does not vibrate the rim or basket.
Roby (OKC) reaches in and makes contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm, which pulls his hand off of the ball and affects his driving shot attempt.
Roby (OKC) makes marginal contact with Carter Jr.'s body (ORL) that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
During the rebound, Roby (OKC) reaches for the ball and avoids contact with Anthony's (ORL) arm as Anthony maintains his pivot foot after stumbling by spinning away from Roby.
Wagner (ORL) slips the pick and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact with Krejci (OKC) during his roll to the basket.
Bazley (OKC) turns into and makes contact with Anthony's (ORL) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Pokusevski (OKC) takes more than 5 seconds to release his inbounds pass.
Wagner (ORL) briefly grasps and immediately releases Krejci's (OKC) jersey as marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Roby (OKC) makes clean ball contact to tap the rebound away from Anthony (ORL).
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Roby's (OKC) path and absorbs the marginal contact during Roby's play at the basket.
Pokusevski (OKC) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).
Anthony (ORL) moves alongside of Mann (OKC) and removes his hand from Mann's path to avoid any marginal contact with his arm during the driving shot attempt.
Roby (OKC) wraps his arms around Wagner's (ORL) body and holds him, which affects his FOM during the inbound.
Krejci (OKC) commits a take foul on Okeke (ORL).
